# Draft:Charles Edward Cullen

Charles Edward Cullen was a political candidate [https://tiaki.natlib.govt.nz/#details=ethesaurus.115238 ]  1965 Christchurch mayoral election 1968 Christchurch mayoral election and WW1 soldier https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/173216224/charles-edward-cullen who stood in the 1965 and 1968 Christchurch mayoral elections in New Zealand as an Independent.
